title: La Villeneuve-en-Chevrie
text: La Villeneuve-en-Chevrie is a <a href="Communes%20of%20France">commune</a> in the <a href="Yvelines">Yvelines</a> <a href="Departments%20of%20France">department</a> in the <a href="%C3%8Ele-de-France%20%28region%29">Île-de-France</a> in north-central <a href="France">France</a>.
